```plantuml
@startuml 2WAY_Design

package "2WAY_Design System" {
    [Trust Network Manager] as TrustManager
    [Data Exchange Engine] as DataEngine
    [Authentication Service] as AuthService
    [Authorization Service] as AuthzService
    [Privacy Module] as PrivacyModule
    [Data Storage] as Storage
    [API Gateway] as APIGateway
}

[External System] as External

TrustManager --> DataEngine : manages
DataEngine --> Storage : reads/writes
DataEngine --> PrivacyModule : applies\nprivacy rules
AuthService --> AuthzService : verifies\npermissions
APIGateway --> AuthService : authenticates\nrequests
APIGateway --> DataEngine : routes\ndata requests
APIGateway --> External : exposes\nAPI endpoints
PrivacyModule --> DataEngine : processes\ndata

note right of TrustManager
  Manages trusted parties
  and connection rules
end note

note left of PrivacyModule
  May implement techniques like
  differential privacy
end note

@enduml
```